#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:1
msgid "如何运行策略优化"
msgstr "Cómo ejecutar la optimización de la estrategia"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:3
msgid "入口与常用 kwargs"
msgstr "Punto de entrada y kwargs comunes"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:5
msgid ""
"使用 **qt.run(op, mode=2, ...)** 运行策略优化。常用参数包括 "
"**opti_method**、**opti_sample_count**、**opti_output_count** 等。"
msgstr ""
"Ejecute la optimización de la estrategia con **``qt.run(op, mode=2, "
"...)``**. Common arguments include **``opti_method``**, "
"**``opti_sample_count``**, **``opti_output_count``** y otros."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:7
msgid "优化算法完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr ""
"Lista completa de algoritmos de optimización (con breves explicaciones)"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:9
msgid "以下为 **opti_method** 常见可选值及适用场景，与 qteasy 2.0 API 一致为准。"
msgstr ""
"Los siguientes son valores **``opti_method``** comunes y casos de uso "
"típicos; Consulte la API qteasy 2.0 como fuente de verdad."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "算法名"
msgstr "Algoritmo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "含义"
msgstr "Significado"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "适用场景"
msgstr "Caso de uso típico"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "grid"
msgstr "grid"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "网格搜索"
msgstr "Búsqueda de cuadrícula"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数少、离散空间，穷举或粗网格。"
msgstr ""
"Pocos parámetros, espacio discreto; Búsqueda de cuadrícula exhaustiva o "
"aproximada."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "montecarlo"
msgstr "montecarlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "蒙特卡洛随机采样"
msgstr "Muestreo aleatorio de Montecarlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数较多时随机抽样评估。"
msgstr "Muestreo aleatorio cuando hay muchos parámetros."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "GA"
msgstr "GA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "遗传算法"
msgstr "Algoritmo genético"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中高维、连续/离散混合。"
msgstr "Dimensiones medias a altas; espacios mixtos continuos/discretos."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "SA"
msgstr "SA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "模拟退火"
msgstr "Recocido simulado"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中维、易陷入局部最优时。"
msgstr ""
"Dimensiones medianas; útil cuando los óptimos locales son una preocupación."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "PSO"
msgstr "PSO"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "粒子群优化"
msgstr "Optimización del enjambre de partículas"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "连续空间、多峰。"
msgstr "Espacio continuo con múltiples picos."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "bayesian"
msgstr "bayesian"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "贝叶斯优化"
msgstr "optimización bayesiana"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "样本昂贵、需少步数寻优。"
msgstr ""
"Evaluaciones costosas; Necesita buenos resultados en unos pocos pasos."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:20
msgid "优化运行参数完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr ""
"Lista completa de parámetros de ejecución de optimización (con breves "
"explicaciones)"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数名"
msgstr "Parámetro"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "类型/可选值"
msgstr "Tipo / Valores"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_method"
msgstr "opti_method"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "str"
msgstr "str"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "优化算法：grid、montecarlo、GA、SA、PSO、bayesian 等。"
msgstr ""
"Algoritmo de optimización: ``grid``, ``montecarlo``, ``GA``, ``SA``, "
"``PSO``, ``bayesian``, etc."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_sample_count"
msgstr "opti_sample_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "int"
msgstr "int"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "采样/迭代次数（如蒙特卡洛样本数、遗传代数等）。"
msgstr ""
"Número de muestras/iteraciones (por ejemplo, muestras de Monte Carlo o "
"generaciones GA)."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_output_count"
msgstr "opti_output_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "保留的最优结果数量（Top-K）。"
msgstr "Número de mejores resultados a conservar (Top-K)."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "目标函数相关"
msgstr "Función objetivo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "—"
msgstr "—"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "如优化目标为夏普、回撤等，以配置或 API 为准。"
msgstr ""
"Por ejemplo, ratio de Sharpe o reducción; consulte los documentos de "
"configuración o API."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "约束相关"
msgstr "Restricciones"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "若有约束（如最大回撤上限），以配置为准。"
msgstr ""
"Si se aplican restricciones (por ejemplo, límite máximo de reducción), "
"consulte la configuración."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:30
msgid "回测区间、asset_pool 等与 mode=1 相同的参数在 mode=2 时同样生效。"
msgstr ""
"Rango de fechas de prueba retrospectiva, ``asset_pool``, and other arguments"
" shared with ``mode=1`` also apply in ``mode=2``."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:32
msgid "参数空间"
msgstr "Espacio de parámetros"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:34
msgid ""
"策略的 **Parameter** 及 **par_range** 定义优化时的搜索空间；框架按 opti_method 在该空间内采样或搜索。"
msgstr ""
"La estrategia es **``Parameter``** objects and **``par_range``** define the "
"search space; the framework samples or searches within it according to "
"``opti_method``."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:36
msgid "最小可运行示例"
msgstr "Ejemplo mínimo ejecutable"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:47
msgid "配置要点"
msgstr "Aspectos destacados de la configuración"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:49
msgid "**回测区间、资产池**：与 mode=1 一致，决定每次参数评估的回测环境。"
msgstr ""
"**Rango de prueba retrospectiva y grupo de activos**: Igual que ``mode=1``; "
"Definen el entorno de backtest para la evaluación de cada parámetro."

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:50
msgid "**目标函数**：决定“更优”的定义（如夏普最大化、回撤最小化），影响排序与最终选取。"
msgstr ""
"**Función objetiva**: Define lo que significa \"mejor\" (por ejemplo, "
"maximizar Sharpe o minimizar la reducción) y afecta la clasificación y la "
"selección final."
